    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Our courses will inspire you and provide the skills and knowledge you need. Our graduates lead the way in their chosen careers. Our researchers are not just cutting-edge and world-leading, they actually make a difference in the real world. Our multidisciplinary staff team really cares.</p>
<p><strong>Everyone deserves the opportunity to communicate.</strong></p>]]></Value>
