      <Value><![CDATA[Division of Speech and Hearing Sciences. We aim to achieve a balance by taking our cutting-edge, world-leading research and helping to make it actually count in the real world. Clinical technologies and other products of research are increasingly in use in clinical environments, but we always want to help you do more, and to tailor our research priorities accordingly. Everyone deserves the opportunity to communicate.]]></Value>
